sub_title: Supplier Quality Management at Philips Healthcare
summary:
I am an experienced Supplier Quality Director at Philips Consumer Lifestyle. I have worked with many different suppliers of various components. I have extensive experience with advanced quality tools. I am managing a world-wide virtual team of Supplier Quality Engineers. I adapt my leadership style to circumstances, local culture and the employees, allowing the people I work with to function and develop in an optimal way. I am hands-on, able to quickly analyze complex problems and able to steer multi-functional teams to come to efficient solutions.

Specialties: Supplier Quality Management
